snippet.title: Re:Awaken - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1358660/ReAwaken/

Purify negativity from the afterlife and bring together the children of fate! Swear oaths to divine beasts and wield powerful twilight abilities in this anime inspired roguelite adventure.
